commentary: Mohammad Hafeez to Smith, OUT Given out lbw but the point of impact was just outside off stump. He went back, shuffled across, and again, like the last game, and even on the previous delivery, stabbed outside the line of the ball, trying to waft across the line. Clueless. The ball landed just outside off and skidded towards off. It would have hit off but the impact was outside off and he was playing a shot.

commentary: Shahid Afridi to Simmons, OUT Umar Akmal takes a stinger at short extra cover! It was floated well outside off, Simmons reached out for it and carved it really hard over that short extra cover but Umar  jumped to pouch it rather calmly! He parried the ball and caught it on the rebound.  Good knock but it's over now.

commentary: Mohammad Hafeez to Edwards, OUT What a mess! It landed outside off and turned in gently. Kirk thought it would explode in and pushed nervously, well inside the line as if he anticipated it would turn in  big. Meanwhile, the ball wobbled away gently towards the off stump. Kirk tried to adjust and moved his wrists to the right. Too late. The ball fell on the off stump. Clatter!

commentary: Martin to Ahmed Shehzad, OUT Shafiq is run out Or is he? It was pushed to point region and Shehzad sets off for the run before he changed his mind. Shafiq had rushed too far across. The fielder came in from backward point and threw to the bowler. Martin lunges to his left to collect it but here begins the drama. He reaches to break the stumps but he missed it! he then lunged again to find the stumps and the bail just about lifted before the bat came inside the crease. It appeared very close. Out is the verdict
